- Multiple shapes may be chained: arrow → shape A → shape B → shape C → grid edge
- Stems have variable width based on their source (arrow stems are 1 wide; shape connector stems match the green connector width)
- Shapes without green connectors are ignored (shouldn't occur in valid inputs)

